	(datasette_trigger_flux_change): Send signal to VIA1.

	* vic20/vic20via2.c, vic20/vic20via.h (mem_set_tape_sense):
	Renamed to `via2_set_tape_sense'.  #include "datasette.h".
	(store_pcr): Added datasette motor signal.

