	* arch/win32/drive.dsp: Added riot1drive1.c and riot2drive1.c.

	* arch/win32/kbd.c: Include "machine.h".
	  (kbd_handle_keyup, kbd_handle_keydown): Call machine_set_restore_key
	  when PGUP is pressed.

